body:

------
I was curious about the popularity of chess variants at [https://lichess.org](https://lichess.org/).

So I grabbed the data from the lichess game [database](https://database.lichess.org/) and created some visualizations.

------


#### <em>Average</em> number of games played per *year* and variant

Let's start with an overview and look at the *average* number of games played per year.





