<center><small>Hover over the heatmap with your mouse for more information.</small></center>

As you can see, the most popular variants happen to be *crazyhouse*, *antichess* and *atomic chess*,
followed by *chess960* and *three-check chess*. Less popular variants include *horde*, *king of the hill* and *racing kings*.

Let's get more specific!

------

#### <em>Total</em> number of games played per *month* and variant

